title: February Brainstorm
author: VD
content_html: Monday at 7 PM EST will be the closed Brainstorm session for February. I’ll be providing a detailed progress report on Operation Big Fork, throwing out some ideas for discussion concerning the next steps, and providing an update of the new developments with regards to Rabid Puppies and a few other things. The invitations will be sent out later today.
